main event: A round-white object, estimated to be 80 feet in diameter, was spotted traveling at 1500 mph over Gateway Intersection, Alabama on March 27, 1954.
interesting points: The object was observed by a single civilian witness., The report from Project Blue Book indicates a high speed for the unidentified object., Essential information was missing in the report, resulting in an insufficient data classification., The encounter occurred at an altitude of 21,222 feet., No photograph was included with the report.
